title: Round the thumbnails
---

%p
  Read about 
  =link_to 'Image Shapes', 'http://getbootstrap.com/css/#images', target: '_blank'
  in the Bootstrap documentation.

%p Replace the line:

= preserve do 
  - code("erb") do
    <td><%= image_tag idea.picture_url if idea.picture? %></td>

%p with this:

= preserve do 
  - code("erb") do
    <td><%= image_tag idea.picture_url, class: 'img-circle' if idea.picture? %></td>

%p Refresh the page and notice that the images are now shaped like circles.
